******
[1] Kenya - RVF alert
Date: Wed 30 May 2018
Source: Daily Nation [edited]
https://www.nation.co.ke/video/news/4146788-4586690-format-xhtml-1uh3dm/index.html


The state has issued an alert over the outbreak of the Rift Valley Fever [RVF] in Rift valley region, advised farmers to vaccinate their livestock against it as a deterrent measure. The principal Secretary for livestock Mr. Harry Kimtai said that there is a looming danger of the disease following the heavy rainfall experienced countrywide noting that county governments should ensure that they roll out a massive vaccination of livestock.

